Subject: [PATCH] Replace requiresRiskMitigation with criticalAlertsDisabled in
 AlertPermissionsChecker

Update the intersection check in NotificationCenterSettingsFlags to use
.criticalAlertsDisabled instead of .requiresRiskMitigation.

https://claude.ai/code/session_01F1wur2rA2PPfF1MYkPPKez
---
 Loop/Managers/AlertPermissionsChecker.swift | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/Loop/Managers/AlertPermissionsChecker.swift b/Loop/Managers/AlertPermissionsChecker.swift
index bae4512e..a0458775 100644
--- a/Loop/Managers/AlertPermissionsChecker.swift
+++ b/Loop/Managers/AlertPermissionsChecker.swift
@@ -228,7 +228,7 @@ extension NotificationCenterSettingsFlags {
         }
     }
     var requiresRiskMitigation: Bool {
-        !self.intersection(.requiresRiskMitigation).isEmpty
+        !self.intersection(.criticalAlertsDisabled).isEmpty
     }
 }
 
